      <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #0369a1; font-weight: 600;">Glutinous Rice Balls → Reunion</p>
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95em;">Round shape symbolizes family togetherness. 圆 means round and sounds like 团圆 (reunion). Eaten on Lantern Festival (Day 15).</p>
